==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Interpoint
<hw>In`ter*point"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To point; to
mark with stops or pauses; to punctuate.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Her sighs should <qex>interpoint</qex> her words.</q>
<rj><qau>Daniel.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Interpolable</ent>⟦br⟧
